        <abstract>
            <p>Invites him to dinner on Saturday the 12th. Charles and Mrs Lyell, Edward Forbes, Richard Owen, and Thomas Bell coming also.</p>
            <p>"Will you bring your map of S. America … and we will have a talk over it."</p>
